s in the\nthermal expansion coefficient and Gr\\\"uneisen parameter \\Gamma are found below\n\\~ 20 K, confirming the results of Chmaissem et al. [Phys. Rev. Lett. 79, 4866\n(1997)] obtained using neutron diffraction. We estimate that \\Gamma(0) is about\n11.4.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Nov 1998 11:55:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-11-12"}
